item.title: Teleport repost
item.dc:creator: @usman555 usman555
item.description:
@usman555 wrote:

how to change where you go in teleport

teleport to catherby
::mypos (this finds out your coords)
search those coords in clickingmost.java
change those coords to where you want to be

remember, when you teleport to catherby, dont move.
